\begin_layout Section
p阶差分方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y_{t}=\phi_{1}y_{t-1}+\phi_{2}y_{t-2}+...+\phi_{p}y_{t-p}+\omega_{t}\tag{1.2.1}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
向量形式。定义(p*1)的向量
\begin_inset Formula $\xi_{t}$
\end_inset

：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi_{t}\equiv\left[\begin{array}{c}
y_{t}\\
y_{t-1}\\
y_{t-2}\\
\vdots\\
y_{t-p+1}
\end{array}\right]\tag{1.2.2}
\]

\end_inset

定义(p*p)的矩阵F为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F\equiv\left[\begin{array}{cccccc}
\phi_{1} & \phi_{2} & \phi_{3} & \cdots & \phi_{p-1} & \phi_{p}\\
1 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0\\
0 & 1 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0\\
\vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \cdots & \vdots & \vdots\\
0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 1 & 0
\end{array}\right]\tag{1.2.3}
\]

\end_inset

定义(p*1)的向量：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v_{t}\equiv\left[\begin{array}{c}
\omega_{t}\\
0\\
0\\
\vdots\\
0
\end{array}\right]\tag{1.2.4}
\]

\end_inset

于是，p阶差分方程可写成：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi_{t}=F\xi_{t-1}+v_{t}\tag{1.2.5}
\]

\end_inset

通过迭代，有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi_{t}=F^{t+1}\xi_{-1}+F^{t}v_{0}+F^{t-1}v_{1}+...+Fv_{t-1}+v_{t}\tag{1.2.6}
\]

\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula $f_{ij}^{(t)}$
\end_inset

表示
\begin_inset Formula $F^{t}$
\end_inset

的第(i,j)个元素，则將上式展开，可得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y_{t}=f_{11}^{(t+1)}y_{-1}+f_{12}^{(t+1)}y_{-2}+...+f_{1p}^{(t+1)}y_{-p}+f_{11}^{(t)}\omega_{0}+f_{11}^{(t-1)}\omega_{1}+...+f_{11}^{(1)}\omega_{t-1}+\omega_{t}\tag{1.2.8}
\]

\end_inset

动态乘子：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}=f_{11}^{(j)}\tag{1.2.11}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
动态乘子——当p阶差分方程的特征值不同时
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
尽管可以通过数值计算或者数值模拟得到动态乘子，但是，我们还是希望进一步了解动态乘子的分析特征。首先回顾矩阵F的特征值
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

满足：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
|F-\lambda I_{p}|=0\tag{1.2.12}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
性质1.1：方程(1.2.3)定义的F的特征值是满足下式的λ值：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lambda^{p}-\phi_{1}\lambda^{p-1}-\phi_{2}\lambda^{p-2}-...-\phi_{p-1}\lambda-\phi_{p}=0\tag{1.2.16}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定(p*p)的矩阵F的特征值各不相同，则存在一个(p*p)的非奇异矩阵T，使得
\begin_inset Formula $F=T\varLambda T^{-1}$
\end_inset

，于是
\begin_inset Formula $F^{j}$
\end_inset

可以写成：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F^{j}=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
t_{11} & t_{12} & \cdots & t_{1p}\\
t_{21} & t_{22} & \cdots & t_{2p}\\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
t_{p1} & t_{p2} & \cdots & t_{pp}
\end{array}\right]\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
\lambda_{1}^{j} & 0 & \cdots & 0\\
0 & \lambda_{2}^{j} & \cdots & 0\\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
0 & 0 & \cdots & \lambda_{p}^{j}
\end{array}\right]\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
t^{11} & t^{12} & \cdots & t^{1p}\\
t^{21} & t^{22} & \cdots & t^{2p}\\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
t^{p1} & t^{p2} & \cdots & t^{pp}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

于是
\begin_inset Formula $F^{j}$
\end_inset

的第(1,1)个元素为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{11}^{(j)}=[t_{11}t^{11}]\lambda_{1}^{j}+[t_{12}t^{21}]\lambda_{2}^{j}+...+[t_{1p}t^{p1}]\lambda_{p}^{j}
\]

\end_inset

或
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{11}^{(j)}=c_{1}\lambda_{1}^{j}+c_{2}\lambda_{2}^{j}+...+c_{p}\lambda_{p}^{j}\tag{1.2.20}
\]

\end_inset

注意到
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}+c_{2}+...+c_{p}=[t_{11}t^{11}]+[t_{12}t^{21}]+...+[t_{1p}t^{p1}]$
\end_inset

，即为
\begin_inset Formula $T*T^{-1}$
\end_inset

的第(1,1)个元素，显然有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
c_{1}+c_{2}+...+c_{p}=1\tag{1.2.23}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
性质1.2 给出常数
\begin_inset Formula $(c_{1},c_{2},...,c_{p})$
\end_inset

的闭型表达式：如果式(1.2.3)中定义的矩阵F的特征值为
\begin_inset Formula $(\lambda_{1},\lambda_{2},...,\lambda_{p})$
\end_inset

是不同的，则
\begin_inset Formula $c_{i}$
\end_inset

可以写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
c_{i}=\frac{\lambda_{i}^{p-1}}{\Pi_{k=1,k\neq i}^{p}(\lambda_{i}-\lambda_{k})}\tag{1.2.25}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
特征值的一些特征
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
如果所有特征值的绝对值均小于1，则系统是稳定的，且系统的动态被表示为指数衰减的加权平均；相反，若存在至少一个特征值的绝对值大于1，则系统是爆炸的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
令
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}$
\end_inset

代表绝对值最大的特征值，动态乘子最终由该特征值的指数函数主导(
\begin_inset Formula $\underset{j\rightarrow\infty}{lim}\frac{\partial y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}\frac{1}{\lambda_{1}^{j}}=c_{1}$
\end_inset

)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
如果存在复数特征值，特征值将以复数共轭的形式出现。以二阶差分方程
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}=\phi_{1}y_{t-1}+\phi_{2}y_{t-2}+\omega_{t}$
\end_inset

为例，并且
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{1}^{2}+4\phi_{2}<0$
\end_inset

，则F对应的特征值为
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}=a+bi$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{2}=a-bi$
\end_inset

，显然
\begin_inset Formula $a=\phi_{1}/2$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $b=(1/2)\sqrt{-\phi_{1}^{2}-4\phi_{2}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
为了將复数转换为幂，先將特征值写成极坐标的形式
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}=R[cos(\theta)+i\cdot sin(\theta)]$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $R=\sqrt{a^{2}+b^{2}}\,,\,cos(\theta)=a/R\,,\,sin(\theta)=b/R$
\end_inset

，于是
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}=R[e^{i\theta}]\Rightarrow\lambda_{1}^{j}=R^{j}[e^{i\theta j}]=R^{j}[cos(\theta j)+i\cdot sin(\theta j)]$
\end_inset

，类似地可得
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{2}^{j}=R^{j}[e^{-i\theta j}]=R^{j}[cos(\theta j)-i\cdot sin(\theta j)]$
\end_inset

，则动态乘子
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
c_{1}\lambda_{1}^{j}+c_{2}\lambda_{2}^{j} & =c_{1}R^{j}[cos(\theta j)+i\cdot sin(\theta j)]+c_{2}R^{j}[cos(\theta j)-i\cdot sin(\theta j)]\\
 & =[c_{1}+c_{2}]R^{j}cos(\theta j)+i\cdot[c_{1}-c_{2}]R^{j}sin(\theta j)\tag{1.2.39}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
巧妙的是：如果
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{2}$
\end_inset

共轭，则
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $c_{2}$
\end_inset

也共轭，即
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $c_{2}$
\end_inset

可写成
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}=\alpha+\beta i\,,\,c_{2}=\alpha-\beta i$
\end_inset

，代入上式得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
c_{1}\lambda_{1}^{j}+c_{2}\lambda_{2}^{j}=2\alpha R^{j}cos(\theta j)-2\beta R^{j}sin(\theta j)
\]

\end_inset

因此，当某些特征值是复数时，动态乘子就是指数与三角函数的复合形态。
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Subsubsection
带有不同特征值的二阶差分方程的解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
动态乘子——当p阶差分方程有重复特征值时
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
考虑更一般的情形：差分方程对应的F矩阵有重复的特征值以及
\begin_inset Formula $s<p$
\end_inset

个线性独立的特征向量，利用约当分解(Jordan decomposition)：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F=MJM^{-1}\tag{1.2.40}
\]

\end_inset

其中，M是(p*p)的矩阵，J的形式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
J=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
J_{1} & 0 & \cdots & 0\\
0 & J_{2} & \cdots & 0\\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
0 & 0 & \cdots & J_{s}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
J_{i}=\left[\begin{array}{cccccc}
\lambda_{i} & 1 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & 0\\
0 & \lambda_{i} & 1 & \cdots & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & \lambda_{i} & \cdots & 0 & 0\\
\vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots & \vdots\\
0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & \lambda_{i} & 1\\
0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & \lambda_{i}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

于是
\begin_inset Formula $F^{j}=MJ^{j}M^{-1}$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
J^{j}=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
J_{1}^{j} & 0 & \cdots & 0\\
0 & J_{2}^{j} & \cdots & 0\\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
0 & 0 & \cdots & J_{s}^{j}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

进一步地，如果
\begin_inset Formula $J_{i}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $n_{i}*n_{i}$
\end_inset

维的，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
J_{i}=\left[\begin{array}{cccccc}
\lambda_{i}^{j} & C_{j}^{1}\lambda_{i}^{j-1} & C_{j}^{2}\lambda_{i}^{j-2} & \cdots & C_{j}^{n_{i}-2}\lambda_{i}^{j-n_{i}+2} & C_{j}^{n_{i}-1}\lambda_{i}^{j-n_{i}+1}\\
0 & \lambda_{i} & C_{j}^{1}\lambda_{i}^{j-1} & \cdots & C_{j}^{n_{i}-3}\lambda_{i}^{j-n_{i}+3} & C_{j}^{n_{i}-2}\lambda_{i}^{j-n_{i}+2}\\
0 & 0 & \lambda_{i} & \cdots & C_{j}^{n_{i}-4}\lambda_{i}^{j-n_{i}+4} & C_{j}^{n_{i}-3}\lambda_{i}^{j-n_{i}+3}\\
\vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots & \vdots\\
0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & \lambda_{i} & \vdots\\
0 & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 & \lambda_{i}
\end{array}\right]
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $C_{n}^{j}\equiv\begin{cases}
\frac{n(n-1)...(n-j+1)}{j!} & \text{，}n\geq j\\
0 & \text{，其他}
\end{cases}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
以二阶差分方程为例，考虑重根的情形，有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F^{j}=M\left[\begin{array}{cc}
\lambda^{j} & j\lambda^{j-1}\\
0 & \lambda^{j}
\end{array}\right]M^{-1}
\]

\end_inset

所以动态乘子的形式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega}=f_{11}^{(j)}=k_{1}\lambda^{j}+k_{2}j\lambda^{j-1}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
长期与现值的计算
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

的变换对
\begin_inset Formula $\xi$
\end_inset

的现值的影响为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}\xi_{t+j}}{\partial v_{t}^{'}}=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}F^{j}=(I_{p}-\beta F)^{-1}\tag{1.2.46}
\]

\end_inset

前提是F的特征值的模小于
\begin_inset Formula $\beta^{-1}$
\end_inset

。于是，
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

的现值的影响为
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\partial\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
性质1.3：若式(1.2.3)定义的(p*p)矩阵F的特征值的模均小于
\begin_inset Formula $\beta^{-1}$
\end_inset

，则矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $(I_{p}-\beta F)^{-1}$
\end_inset

存在，且
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

的现值的影响有该矩阵的第(1,1)个元素确定
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{1-\phi_{1}\beta-\phi_{2}\beta^{2}-...-\phi_{p-1}\beta^{p-1}-\phi_{p}\beta^{p}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\omega_{t}$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t},y_{t+1},...$
\end_inset

的累积效应可以看作性质1.3没有折现的特例
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}=\frac{1}{1-\phi_{1}-\phi_{2}-...-\phi_{p-1}-\phi_{p}}\tag{1.2.47}
\]

\end_inset

式(1.2.47)还可以解释为
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

的永久变化对
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

的长期影响(长期乘子)
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underset{j\rightarrow\infty}{lim}\sum_{i=0}^{j}\frac{\partial y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t+i}}=\frac{1}{1-\phi_{1}-\phi_{2}-...-\phi_{p-1}-\phi_{p}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
滞后算子
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
简介
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $Lx_{t}\equiv x_{t-1}$
\end_inset

 → 对于任意的整数k，
\begin_inset Formula $L^{k}x_{t}=x_{t-k}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
滞后算子复合乘法的代数运算法则。当面对一个时间序列的复合运算，我们可以灵活运用交换律、结合律和分配律等加法和乘法的代数运算法则，进而将原始变为另外一种形式。
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
交换律：
\begin_inset Formula $L(\beta x_{t})=\beta\cdot Lx_{t}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
分配律：
\begin_inset Formula $L(x_{t}+y_{t})=Lx_{t}+Ly_{t}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Section
一阶差分方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
首先，將一阶差分方程
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}=\phi y_{t-1}+\omega_{t}$
\end_inset

改写成包含滞后算子的形式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi L)y_{t}=\omega_{t}\tag{2.2.2}
\]

\end_inset

考虑在等式两边同时乘以
\begin_inset Formula $(1+\phi L+\phi^{2}L^{2}+...+\phi^{t}L^{t})$
\end_inset

，整理后得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi^{t+1}L^{t+1})y_{t}=(1+\phi L+\phi^{2}L^{2}+...+\phi^{t}L^{t})\omega_{t}\tag{2.2.6}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y=\phi^{t+1}y_{-1}+\omega_{t}+\phi\omega_{t-1}+...+\phi^{t}\omega_{0}\tag{2.2.7}
\]

\end_inset

注意到使用滞后算子
\begin_inset Formula $(1+\phi L+\phi^{2}L^{2}+...+\phi^{t}L^{t})$
\end_inset

和前一章节中运用递归替代法的结果是一样的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
在上式中，当
\begin_inset Formula $|\phi|<1$
\end_inset

且
\begin_inset Formula $y_{-1}$
\end_inset

是一个有限的数，则
\begin_inset Formula $\phi^{t+1}y_{-1}$
\end_inset

会随着t的增加而减小：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1+\phi L+\phi^{2}L^{2}+...+\phi^{t}L^{t})(1-\phi L)y_{t}\cong y_{t}\text{，}t\text{足够大}
\]

\end_inset

作为算子
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\phi L)$
\end_inset

[【
\begin_inset Formula $|\phi|<1$
\end_inset

】的倒数的估计值，当j足够大时，这个估计值满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi L)^{-1}=\underset{j\rightarrow\infty}{lim}(1+\phi L+\phi^{2}L^{2}+...+\phi^{j}L^{j})\tag{2.2.8}
\]

\end_inset

算子
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\phi L)^{-1}$
\end_inset

满足性质
\begin_inset Formula $(1-\phi L)^{-1}(1-\phi L)=1$
\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
二阶差分方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
考虑一个二阶差分方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y_{t}=\phi_{1}y_{t-1}+\phi_{2}y_{t-2}+\omega_{t}\tag{2.3.1}
\]

\end_inset

改写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2})y_{t}=(1-\lambda_{1}L)(1-\lambda_{2}L)y_{t}=\omega_{t}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
p阶差分方程
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
考虑一个p阶差分方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y_{t}=\phi_{1}y_{t-1}+\phi_{2}y_{t-2}+...+\phi_{p}y_{t-p}+\omega_{t}\tag{2.4.1}
\]

\end_inset

改写成,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p})y_{t}=(1-\lambda_{1}L)(1-\lambda_{2}L)...(1-\lambda_{p}L)y_{t}=\omega_{t}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
性质2.2 ：將p阶差分方程的滞后算子形式因式分解如下
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p})=(1-\lambda_{1}L)(1-\lambda_{2}L)...(1-\lambda_{p}L)\tag{2.4.3}
\]

\end_inset

其计算与求式(1.2.3)定义的F的特征值相同。F的特征值
\begin_inset Formula $(\lambda_{1},\lambda_{2},...,\lambda_{p})$
\end_inset

与式(2.4.3)中的系数
\begin_inset Formula $(\lambda_{1},\lambda_{2},...,\lambda_{p})$
\end_inset

完全相同，并且由下面方程的给出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lambda^{p}-\phi_{1}\lambda^{p-1}-\phi_{2}\lambda^{p-2}-...-\phi_{p-1}\lambda-\phi_{p}=0\tag{2.4.5}
\]

\end_inset

解法可见原书。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
一个计算
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

现值的影响更为简单的方法
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
首先，
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}=\psi_{0}\omega_{t}+\psi_{1}\omega_{t-1}+...$
\end_inset

，其中，
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{j}=c_{1}\lambda_{1}^{j}+c_{2}\lambda_{2}^{j}+...+c_{p}\lambda_{p}^{j}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
將上式写成滞后算子形式：
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}=\psi(L)\omega_{t}$
\end_inset

，其中，
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(L)=\psi_{0}+\psi_{1}L+\psi_{2}L^{2}+...$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\omega_{t}$
\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

现值的影响：
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\partial\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}\frac{\partial y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}\psi_{j}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
当考虑z取实数时，多项式
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(z)$
\end_inset

变为：
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(z)=\psi_{0}+\psi_{1}z+\psi_{2}z^{2}+...$
\end_inset

，注意到上式的结果恰好是
\begin_inset Formula $z=\beta$
\end_inset

时的多项式的值，即
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\partial\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}=\psi(\beta)=\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}\psi_{j}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
通过对比
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}=\psi(L)\omega_{t}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}=[(1-\lambda_{1}L)(1-\lambda_{2}L)...(1-\lambda_{p}L)]^{-1}\omega_{t}$
\end_inset

发现
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(L)=[(1-\lambda_{1}L)(1-\lambda_{2}L)...(1-\lambda_{p}L)]^{-1}$
\end_inset

，这意味着
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(L)=[1-\phi_{1}L-\phi_{2}L^{2}-...-\phi_{p}L^{p}]^{-1}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
于是，
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(\beta)=[1-\phi_{1}\beta-\phi_{2}\beta^{2}-...-\phi_{p}\beta^{p}]^{-1}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
结果，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\beta^{j}y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t}}=\frac{1}{1-\phi_{1}\beta-\phi_{2}\beta^{2}-...-\phi_{p-1}\beta^{p-1}-\phi_{p}\beta^{p}}
\]

\end_inset

长期乘子就是
\begin_inset Formula $\beta=1$
\end_inset

时的特例
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underset{j\rightarrow\infty}{lim}\sum_{i=0}^{j}\frac{\partial y_{t+j}}{\partial\omega_{t+i}}=\frac{1}{1-\phi_{1}-\phi_{2}-...-\phi_{p-1}-\phi_{p}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
