\begin_layout Section
自回归移动平均过程的和
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
MA(1)过程加白噪声的和
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定一个序列
\begin_inset Formula $X_{t}$
\end_inset

服从零均值MA(1)过程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
X_{t}=u_{t}+\delta u_{t-1}\tag{4.7.1}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}$
\end_inset

是白噪声。令
\begin_inset Formula $v_{t}$
\end_inset

代表另外一个白噪声序列，且假定v和u对于所有超前和滞后都不相关：
\begin_inset Formula $E(u_{i}v_{j})=0$
\end_inset

对于所有i、j均成立。于是
\begin_inset Formula $E(X_{i}v_{j})=0$
\end_inset

对所有i、j均成立
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
令序列
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=X_{t}+v_{t}=u_{t}+\delta u_{t-1}+v_{t}\tag{4.7.5}
\]

\end_inset

则
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
E(Y_{t}Y_{t-j}) & =E(X_{t}X_{t-j})+E(v_{t}v_{t-j})\\
 & =\begin{cases}
(1+\delta^{2})\sigma_{u}^{2}+\sigma_{v}^{2} & \text{，}j=0\\
\delta\sigma_{u}^{2} & \text{，}j=\pm1\\
0 & \text{，}\text{其他}
\end{cases}\tag{4.7.6}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

因此，序列
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}$
\end_inset

是平稳的，且超过一阶的自协方差为0，因此一个很自然的问题是：序列
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}$
\end_inset

是否存在一个MA(1)表示，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{t}=\varepsilon_{t}+\theta\varepsilon_{t-1}
\]

\end_inset

于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E(Y_{t}Y_{t-j})=\begin{cases}
(1+\theta^{2})\sigma^{2} & \text{，}j=0\\
\theta\sigma^{2} & \text{，}j=\pm1\\
0 & \text{，}\text{其他}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

此式要与(4.7.6)完全一致，于是有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
(1+\theta^{2})\sigma^{2} & =(1+\delta^{2})\sigma_{u}^{2}+\sigma_{v}^{2}\\
\theta\sigma^{2} & =\delta\sigma_{u}^{2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

整理得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\delta\theta^{2}-[(1+\delta^{2})+(\delta_{v}^{2}/\delta_{u}^{2})]\theta+\delta=0\tag{4.7.11}
\]

\end_inset

解得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\theta=\frac{[(1+\delta^{2})+(\delta_{v}^{2}/\delta_{u}^{2})]\pm\sqrt{[(1+\delta^{2})+(\delta_{v}^{2}/\delta_{u}^{2})]^{2}-4\delta^{2}}}{2\delta}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
当
\begin_inset Formula $\delta_{v}^{2}=0$
\end_inset

，式(4.7.11)中变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\delta\theta^{2}-(1+\delta^{2})\theta+\delta=\delta(\theta-\delta)(\theta-\delta^{-1})=0\tag{4.7.13}
\]

\end_inset

显然
\begin_inset Formula $f(\theta)=\delta\theta^{2}-[(1+\delta^{2})+(\delta_{v}^{2}/\delta_{u}^{2})]\theta+\delta$
\end_inset

的图像始终在
\begin_inset Formula $g(\theta)=\delta\theta^{2}-(1+\delta^{2})\theta+\delta$
\end_inset

的下方(
\begin_inset Formula $\delta>0$
\end_inset

)
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\text{此处应该有一张图，没有就找原教材吧！\textasciicircum\_\textasciicircum!!!}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
从上图中可以看出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
0<|\theta^{*}|<|\delta|<1<|\delta^{-1}|<|\tilde{\theta}^{*}|
\]

\end_inset

我们取可逆表示相应的(
\begin_inset Formula $\theta^{*},\sigma^{*2}$
\end_inset

)值，即：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1+\theta^{*}L)\varepsilon_{t}=(1+\delta L)u_{t}+v_{t}\tag{4.7.15}
\]

\end_inset

或
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varepsilon_{t}=(1+\theta^{*}L)^{-1}[(1+\delta L)u_{t}+v_{t}]\tag{4.7.16}
\]

\end_inset

可以证明此时定义的
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

序列是白噪声：
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Y序列的自协方差生成函数：
\begin_inset Formula $g_{Y}(z)=(1+\delta z)\sigma_{u}^{2}(1+\delta z^{-1})+\sigma_{v}^{2}$
\end_inset

或者
\begin_inset Formula $g_{Y}(z)=(1+\theta^{*}z)\sigma^{*2}(1+\theta^{*}z^{-1})$
\end_inset

，于是，
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{t}$
\end_inset

的自协方差生成函数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{\varepsilon}(z)=\frac{(1+\delta z)\sigma_{u}^{2}(1+\delta z^{-1})+\sigma_{v}^{2}}{(1+\theta^{*}z)(1+\theta^{*}z^{-1})}=\sigma^{*2}\tag{4.7.18}
\]

\end_inset

得证
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
注意，基于
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}$
\end_inset

过去值的最优预测和基于
\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $v_{t}$
\end_inset

过去值的最优预测是不一样的。一般来说，Y过去值包含的信息较u和v的过去值包含的信息更少；以
\begin_inset Formula $\{Y_{t}\}$
\end_inset

为基础只能估计两个参数
\begin_inset Formula $\theta^{*}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{*2}$
\end_inset

，然而真实模型有三个参数
\begin_inset Formula $\delta,\sigma_{u}^{2},\sigma_{v}^{2}$
\end_inset

，也就是说，结构是不可识别的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
两个移动平均过程相加
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定
\begin_inset Formula $X_{t}$
\end_inset

是一个零均值
\begin_inset Formula $MA(q_{1})$
\end_inset

过程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
X_{t}=(1+\delta_{1}L+\delta_{2}L^{2}+...+\delta_{q_{1}}L^{q_{1}})u_{t}\equiv\delta(L)u_{t}
\]

\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula $W_{t}$
\end_inset

是一个零均值
\begin_inset Formula $MA(q_{2})$
\end_inset

过程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{t}=(1+\kappa_{1}L+\kappa_{2}L^{2}+...+\kappa_{q_{2}}L^{\kappa_{q_{2}}})v_{t}\equiv\kappa(L)v_{t}
\]

\end_inset

假定X和W对每一个超前和滞后都不相关：
\begin_inset Formula $E(X_{t}W_{t-j})=0$
\end_inset

对任意j均成立。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定我们观察到
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}=X_{t}+W_{t}$
\end_inset

，定义
\begin_inset Formula $q=max\{q_{1},q_{2}\}$
\end_inset

，则Y的第j阶自协方差为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
E(Y_{t}Y_{t-j}) & =E(X_{t}X_{t-j})+E(W_{t}W_{t-j})\\
 & \begin{cases}
\gamma_{j}^{X}+\gamma_{j}^{W} & \text{，}j=0,\pm1,\pm2,...,\pm q\\
0 & \text{，}\text{其他}
\end{cases}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
由于
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma_{j}^{Y}=\gamma_{j}^{X}+\gamma_{j}^{W}
\]

\end_inset

于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}\gamma_{j}^{Y}z^{j}=\sum_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}\gamma_{j}^{X}z^{j}+\sum_{j=-\infty}^{\infty}\gamma_{j}^{W}z^{j}
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{Y}(z)=g_{X}(z)+g_{W}(z)\tag{4.7.19}
\]

\end_inset

因此问题就是：是否存在
\begin_inset Formula $(\theta_{1},\theta_{2},...,\theta_{q},\sigma^{2})$
\end_inset

使得(4.7.19)满足：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\theta(z)\theta(z^{-1})\sigma^{2}=\delta(z)\delta(z^{-1})\sigma_{u}^{2}+\kappa(z)\kappa(z^{-1})\sigma_{v}^{2}\tag{4.7.20}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
上述问题的答案是：结果总是存在的。因此对于两个MA过程，只要它们关于所有的超前和滞后都不相关，则二者相加后，其结果是一个新的MA，且新的MA的阶数为两个原始序列
中较大的一个：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
MA(q_{1})+MA(q_{2})=MA(max\{q_{1},q_{2}\})\tag{4.7.21}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
两个AR过程相加
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
假定
\begin_inset Formula $X_{t}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $W_{t}$
\end_inset

是两个
\begin_inset Formula $AR(1)$
\end_inset

过程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
(1-\pi L)X_{t} & =u_{t}\tag{4.7.22}\\
(1-\rho L)W_{t} & =v_{t}\tag{4.7.23}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $v_{t}$
\end_inset

都是白噪声且对于所有的
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $u_{t}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $v_{t}$
\end_inset

无关。再假定我们观测到
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}$
\end_inset

，而实际上
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{t}=X_{t}+W_{t}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
如果恰巧X和W的自回归参数是一样的，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\pi L)(X_{t}+W_{t})=u_{t}+v_{t}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
更一般的情况是两个自回归参数不同，因此我们对(4.7.22-23)两式进行简单的变换：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
(1-\rho L)(1-\pi L)X_{t} & =(1-\rho L)u_{t}\tag{4.7.24}\\
(1-\rho L)(1-\pi L)W_{t} & =(1-\pi L)v_{t}\tag{4.7.25}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

两式相加
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\rho L)(1-\pi L)(X_{t}+W_{t})=(1-\rho L)u_{t}+(1-\pi L)v_{t}
\]

\end_inset

由前述内容可知，上式右侧有一个MA(1)表示，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(1-\rho L)(1-\pi L)(X_{t}+W_{t})=(1+\theta L)\varepsilon_{t}
\]

\end_inset

换句话说
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
AR(1)+AR(1)=ARMA(2,1)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
将上述内容进行推广：将一个
\begin_inset Formula $AR(p_{1})$
\end_inset

过程和一个与其超前和滞后项不相关的
\begin_inset Formula $AR(p_{2})$
\end_inset

过程相加，得到一个
\begin_inset Formula $ARMA(p_{1}+p_{2},max\{p_{1},p_{2}\})$
\end_inset

过程
\end_layout

