\]

\end_inset

也可以等价地写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{-\pi}^{\pi}s_{Y}(\omega)cos(\omega k)d\omega=\gamma_{k}\tag{6.1.16}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

