\frac{1}{T^{3}}\sum_{t=1}^{T}ty_{t-1}^{2}=\frac{1}{T^{2}}\sum_{t=1}^{T}(t/T)y_{t-1}^{2}\overset{L}{\rightarrow}\sigma^{2}\int_{0}^{1}r[W(r)]^{2}dr\tag{17.3.24}
\]

\end_inset


