\]

\end_inset

于是可以计算左边的统计量，进行统计推断。当然，也可以利用OLS估计t检验统计量进行检验：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
t_{T} & =\frac{\hat{\rho}_{T}-1}{\hat{\sigma}_{\hat{\rho}_{T}}}=\frac{T(\hat{\rho}_{T}-1)}{\{T^{2}\cdot\hat{\sigma}_{\hat{\rho}_{T}}^{2}\}^{1/2}}\\
 & \overset{p}{\rightarrow}\left\{ \frac{\frac{1}{2}\{[W(1)]^{2}-1\}-W(1)\int_{0}^{1}W(r)dr}{\int_{0}^{1}[W(r)]^{2}dr-[\int_{0}^{1}W(r)dr]^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}(T^{2}\cdot\hat{\sigma}_{\hat{\rho}_{T}}^{2}/s_{T}^{2})\cdot(\lambda^{2}-\gamma_{0})\right\} /\{T^{2}\cdot\hat{\sigma}_{\hat{\rho}_{T}}^{2}\}^{1/2}\\
