\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{\gamma}_{j}=\frac{1}{T}\sum_{j+1}^{T}\hat{u}_{t}\hat{u}_{t-j}\tag{17.6.17}
\]

\end_inset


