z_{t}^{*}\\
\boldsymbol{u}_{2t}
\end{array}\right]=\boldsymbol{\Psi}^{*}(L)\boldsymbol{\varepsilon}_{t}\tag{19.2.11}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\varepsilon}_{t}$
\end_inset

是一个零均值
\begin_inset Formula $(n\times1)$
\end_inset

iid向量，其四阶矩有限，正定方差-协方差矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $E(\boldsymbol{\varepsilon}_{t}\boldsymbol{\varepsilon}_{t}')=\boldsymbol{P}\boldsymbol{P}'$
\end_inset

。进一步假定
\begin_inset Formula $(n\times n)$
\end_inset

