\begin_inset Formula $\{s\cdot\boldsymbol{\Psi}_{s}^{*}\}_{s=0}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

是绝对可加的，且
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\Psi}^{*}(1)$
\end_inset

的各行是线性无关的。令
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\alpha}_{T}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\boldsymbol{\gamma}}_{T}$
\end_inset

为基于式(19.2.9)的OLS估计的值，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\begin{array}{c}
\hat{\alpha}_{T}\\
\hat{\boldsymbol{\gamma}}_{T}
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
T & \sum\boldsymbol{y}_{2t}'\\
\sum\boldsymbol{y}_{2t} & \sum\boldsymbol{y}_{2t}\boldsymbol{y}_{2t}'
\end{array}\right]^{-1}\left[\begin{array}{c}
\sum y_{1t}\\
\sum\boldsymbol{y}_{2t}y_{1t}
\end{array}\right]\tag{19.2.12}
\]

\end_inset

